Priority: optional
Maintainer: Ryszard Lach <rla@debian.org>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 4.0.2), apache2-threaded-dev (>= 2.0.54-5), libldap2-dev, libsasl2-dev
Standards-Version: 3.6.1

Package: libapache2-mod-ldapcfg
Architecture: any
Depends: apache2.2-common (>= 2.2.3), ${shlibs:Depends}, libldap2.4
Conflicts: libapache2-mod-vhost-ldap
Description: LDAP configuration module for Apache 2
 This module is used to dynamically query configuration directives from
 an LDAP directory on server startup. Useful for distributed
 configuration management.
